				p Phantachat is an online chat service designed to mimic the way humans converse in real life. Existing text based communication apps such as email and instant message save your message history which encourages asynchronous communication. To bring online communication back to a more intimate level, phantachat sends your message in real time as you are typing and does not save any chat history. Each message is displayed on screen for a few seconds before disappearing. This behavior promotes synchronous communication where the recipient is expected to be online at the same time actively engaging in the conversation.
